<donors class="MCRMetaLangText" heritable="false" notinherit="false"><donor xml:lang="en" inherited="0" form="plain">Original names of donors have been erased and sometimes replaced with that of Wälätta Śǝllase (e.g., fols. 20va, 24rb) in Additio 1 and the supplication formulas on fols. 3ra-113vb (hand a).   The names of Gäbrä Mikaʾel and Wäldä Mikaʾel are written in the supplication formulas on fols. 115ra-130vb (hand b).</donor>
