<txstates class="MCRMetaLangText" heritable="false" notinherit="false"><txstate xml:lang="en" inherited="0" form="plain">The Ms. is worn and shows traces of intensive use.&#13;
Many fols. are stained with wax and dirt.&#13;
The Ms. has probably been rebound and resewn.&#13;
The spine cover is missing, most probably cut off to facilitate the resewing.&#13;
The sewing is damaged and crudely repaired.&#13;
Traces of an overback are preserved on the inner side of both boards.&#13;
Fols. 115-118 are of smaller size.</txstate>
</txstates>
